        "建议：Pair the proprietary WF Visual Sans family across every typographic role。",
        "建议：Use {rounded.sm} 4 px for buttons, {rounded.md} 8 px for cards. The brand never uses pill CTAs。"
      ],
      "dont": [
        "避免：promote button-medium weight to 700+. The brand's weight ceiling is 600。",
